  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This quantitative study aimed to evaluate the respiratory muscle strength, pulmonary
      function, cardiovascular function, and impact on quality of life in patients after cardiac
      rehabilitation associated with the diaphragmatic muscle training.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
